data.description: Perfect starter home in a great location. Cozy 3/2 one story home with beautiful open concept layout and high ceiling living room. Roof was recently replaced, New Ac and heating system, primary bathroom, front door and chimney have been upgraded. Fence has been partially replaced. Bring your cosmetic touches to create the perfect home. Conveniently located close to Beltway 8, I-45 and 249. Within minutes from major supermarkets, restaurants, schools and more.  Never flooded per seller and not in a Flood zone.  Buyer to independently verify information.
